# 🎯 Project Objective

Deploy a production-style **3-Tier Architecture** on AWS using Terraform.

The architecture consists of:

### Presentation Layer

* Application Load Balancer (ALB)

### Application Layer

* EC2 Application Servers

### Database Layer

* Amazon RDS MySQL

Infrastructure is provisioned entirely through Terraform code.

