# 🌐 Verification

## Verify VPC

AWS Console → VPC

Expected:

```text
VPC Created
Subnet Created
Route Tables Created
Internet Gateway Attached
```

---

## Verify EC2

AWS Console → EC2

Expected:

```text
2 EC2 Instances Running
Apache Installed
```

---

## Verify Application Load Balancer

Retrieve ALB DNS:

```bash
terraform output
```

Example:

```text
alb_dns =
my-alb-123.ap-south-1.elb.amazonaws.com
```

Open browser:

```text
http://ALB-DNS
```

Expected:

```text
Welcome to Three Tier App
```

---

## Verify RDS

AWS Console → RDS

Expected:

```text
Status = Available
```

Connect from EC2:

```bash
mysql -h endpoint -u admin -p
```

